query:

  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  teamName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  wins INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,

  lastUpdated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)
